[
  {
    "startTime": 17.682,
    "endTime": 21.788999999999998,
    "text": "I come to you today to speak of liars,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.789,
    "endTime": 23.236,
    "text": "lawsuits"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.236,
    "endTime": 25.51,
    "text": "and laughter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.51,
    "endTime": 28.644000000000002,
    "text": "The first time I heard about Holocaust denial,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.644,
    "endTime": 30.569999999999997,
    "text": "I laughed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.57,
    "endTime": 32.787,
    "text": "Holocaust denial?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.787,
    "endTime": 36.241,
    "text": "The Holocaust which has the dubious distinction"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.241,
    "endTime": 41.646,
    "text": "of being the best-documented genocide in the world?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.646,
    "endTime": 44.706,
    "text": "Who could believe it didn't happen?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.706,
    "endTime": 46.857,
    "text": "Think about it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.857,
    "endTime": 49.162,
    "text": "For deniers to be right,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.162,
    "endTime": 51.611,
    "text": "who would have to be wrong?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.611,
    "endTime": 54.400999999999996,
    "text": "Well, first of all, the victims --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.401,
    "endTime": 60.321000000000005,
    "text": "the survivors who have told us their harrowing stories."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.321,
    "endTime": 62.659,
    "text": "Who else would have to be wrong?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.659,
    "endTime": 64.636,
    "text": "The bystanders."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.636,
    "endTime": 68.63799999999999,
    "text": "The people who lived in the myriads of towns and villages and cities"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.638,
    "endTime": 70.634,
    "text": "on the Eastern front,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.634,
    "endTime": 73.1,
    "text": "who watched their neighbors be rounded up --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.1,
    "endTime": 76.33699999999999,
    "text": "men, women, children, young, old --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.337,
    "endTime": 79.081,
    "text": "and be marched to the outskirts of the town"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.081,
    "endTime": 82.58500000000001,
    "text": "to be shot and left dead in ditches."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.585,
    "endTime": 83.939,
    "text": "Or the Poles,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.939,
    "endTime": 88.64399999999999,
    "text": "who lived in towns and villages around the death camps,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.644,
    "endTime": 91.04400000000001,
    "text": "who watched day after day"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.044,
    "endTime": 93.81,
    "text": "as the trains went in filled with people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.81,
    "endTime": 96.387,
    "text": "and came out empty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.387,
    "endTime": 100.605,
    "text": "But above all, who would have to be wrong?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.605,
    "endTime": 102.712,
    "text": "The perpetrators."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.712,
    "endTime": 106.07900000000001,
    "text": "The people who say, \"We did it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.079,
    "endTime": 107.627,
    "text": "I did it.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.627,
    "endTime": 109.8,
    "text": "Now, maybe they add a caveat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.8,
    "endTime": 114.704,
    "text": "They say, \"I didn't have a choice; I was forced to do it.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.704,
    "endTime": 118.538,
    "text": "But nonetheless, they say, \"I did it.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.538,
    "endTime": 120.113,
    "text": "Think about it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.113,
    "endTime": 126.076,
    "text": "In not one war crimes trial since the end of World War II"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.076,
    "endTime": 133.678,
    "text": "has a perpetrator of any nationality ever said, \"It didn't happen.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.678,
    "endTime": 138.284,
    "text": "Again, they may have said, \"I was forced,\" but never that it didn't happen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.284,
    "endTime": 139.78199999999998,
    "text": "Having thought that through,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.782,
    "endTime": 143.757,
    "text": "I decided denial was not going to be on my agenda;"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.757,
    "endTime": 147.489,
    "text": "I had bigger things to worry about, to write about, to research,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.489,
    "endTime": 149.511,
    "text": "and I moved on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.511,
    "endTime": 152.35399999999998,
    "text": "Fast-forward a little over a decade,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.354,
    "endTime": 154.19000000000003,
    "text": "and two senior scholars --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.19,
    "endTime": 157.37199999999999,
    "text": "two of the most prominent historians of the Holocaust --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.372,
    "endTime": 158.65300000000002,
    "text": "approached me and said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.653,
    "endTime": 160.46599999999998,
    "text": "\"Deborah, let's have coffee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.466,
    "endTime": 164.08700000000002,
    "text": "We have a research idea that we think is perfect for you.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.087,
    "endTime": 167.944,
    "text": "Intrigued and flattered that they came to me with an idea"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.944,
    "endTime": 169.545,
    "text": "and thought me worthy of it,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.545,
    "endTime": 172.265,
    "text": "I asked, \"What is it?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.265,
    "endTime": 175.95299999999997,
    "text": "And they said, \"Holocaust denial.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.953,
    "endTime": 178.936,
    "text": "And for the second time, I laughed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.936,
    "endTime": 180.88400000000001,
    "text": "Holocaust denial?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.884,
    "endTime": 182.89399999999998,
    "text": "The Flat Earth folks?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.894,
    "endTime": 185.055,
    "text": "The Elvis-is-alive people?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.055,
    "endTime": 187.92600000000002,
    "text": "I should study them?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.926,
    "endTime": 189.267,
    "text": "And these two guys said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.267,
    "endTime": 191.612,
    "text": "\"Yeah, we're intrigued."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.612,
    "endTime": 193.208,
    "text": "What are they about?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.208,
    "endTime": 194.982,
    "text": "What's their objective?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.982,
    "endTime": 199.356,
    "text": "How do they manage to get people to believe what they say?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.356,
    "endTime": 202.908,
    "text": "So thinking, if they thought it was worthwhile,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.908,
    "endTime": 206.30599999999998,
    "text": "I would take a momentary diversion --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.306,
    "endTime": 209.268,
    "text": "maybe a year, maybe two, three, maybe even four --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.268,
    "endTime": 211.537,
    "text": "in academic terms, that's momentary."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.537,
    "endTime": 212.703,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.703,
    "endTime": 215.114,
    "text": "We work very slowly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.114,
    "endTime": 216.71,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.71,
    "endTime": 218.536,
    "text": "And I would look at them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.536,
    "endTime": 219.715,
    "text": "So I did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.715,
    "endTime": 222.578,
    "text": "I did my research, and I came up with a number of things,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.578,
    "endTime": 225.195,
    "text": "two of which I'd like to share with you today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.195,
    "endTime": 226.552,
    "text": "One:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.552,
    "endTime": 232.31199999999998,
    "text": "deniers are wolves in sheep's clothing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.312,
    "endTime": 235.30100000000002,
    "text": "They are the same: Nazis, Neo-Nazis --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.301,
    "endTime": 239.386,
    "text": "you can decide whether you want to put a \"Neo\" there or not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.386,
    "endTime": 241.743,
    "text": "But when I looked at them,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.743,
    "endTime": 246.493,
    "text": "I didn't see any SS-like uniforms,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.493,
    "endTime": 249.668,
    "text": "swastika-like symbols on the wall,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.668,
    "endTime": 251.749,
    "text": "Sieg Heil salutes --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.749,
    "endTime": 253.317,
    "text": "none of that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.317,
    "endTime": 256.211,
    "text": "What I found instead"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.211,
    "endTime": 261.516,
    "text": "were people parading as respectable academics."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.516,
    "endTime": 262.761,
    "text": "What did they have?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.761,
    "endTime": 264.483,
    "text": "They had an institute."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.483,
    "endTime": 268.992,
    "text": "An \"Institute for Historical Review.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.992,
    "endTime": 271.57,
    "text": "They had a journal -- a slick journal --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.57,
    "endTime": 274.998,
    "text": "a \"Journal of Historical Review.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.998,
    "endTime": 277.728,
    "text": "One filled with papers --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.728,
    "endTime": 280.523,
    "text": "footnote-laden papers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.523,
    "endTime": 283.1,
    "text": "And they had a new name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.1,
    "endTime": 285.29200000000003,
    "text": "Not Neo-Nazis,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.292,
    "endTime": 287.806,
    "text": "not anti-Semites --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.806,
    "endTime": 289.591,
    "text": "revisionists."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.591,
    "endTime": 291.83,
    "text": "They said, \"We are revisionists."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.83,
    "endTime": 294.537,
    "text": "We are out to do one thing:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.537,
    "endTime": 298.969,
    "text": "to revise mistakes in history.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.969,
    "endTime": 304.403,
    "text": "But all you had to do was go one inch below the surface,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.403,
    "endTime": 306.334,
    "text": "and what did you find there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.334,
    "endTime": 308.848,
    "text": "The same adulation of Hitler,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.848,
    "endTime": 310.747,
    "text": "praise of the Third Reich,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.747,
    "endTime": 314.504,
    "text": "anti-Semitism, racism, prejudice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.504,
    "endTime": 316.97400000000005,
    "text": "This is what intrigued me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.974,
    "endTime": 325.33,
    "text": "It was anti-Semitism, racism, prejudice, parading as rational discourse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.33,
    "endTime": 327.163,
    "text": "The other thing I found --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.163,
    "endTime": 331.171,
    "text": "and we saw a slide earlier about facts and opinions --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.171,
    "endTime": 334.94,
    "text": "many of us have been taught to think there are facts and there are opinions --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.94,
    "endTime": 336.42,
    "text": "after studying deniers,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.42,
    "endTime": 338.31800000000004,
    "text": "I think differently."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.318,
    "endTime": 339.99,
    "text": "There are facts,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.99,
    "endTime": 341.728,
    "text": "there are opinions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.728,
    "endTime": 344.029,
    "text": "and there are lies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.029,
    "endTime": 349.445,
    "text": "And what deniers want to do is take their lies,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.445,
    "endTime": 351.101,
    "text": "dress them up as opinions --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.101,
    "endTime": 353.115,
    "text": "maybe edgy opinions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.115,
    "endTime": 355.848,
    "text": "maybe sort of out-of-the-box opinions --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.848,
    "endTime": 357.25600000000003,
    "text": "but then if they're opinions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.256,
    "endTime": 359.412,
    "text": "they should be part of the conversation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.412,
    "endTime": 364.185,
    "text": "And then they encroach on the facts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.185,
    "endTime": 365.772,
    "text": "I published my work --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 365.772,
    "endTime": 366.96999999999997,
    "text": "the book was published,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.97,
    "endTime": 370.396,
    "text": "\"Denying the Holocaust: The Growing Assault on Truth and Memory,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370.396,
    "endTime": 372.37600000000003,
    "text": "it came out in many different countries,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.376,
    "endTime": 374.56,
    "text": "including here in Penguin UK,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.56,
    "endTime": 379.043,
    "text": "and I was done with those folks and ready to move on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.043,
    "endTime": 383.314,
    "text": "Then came the letter from Penguin UK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.314,
    "endTime": 387.968,
    "text": "And for the third time, I laughed ..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.968,
    "endTime": 389.85200000000003,
    "text": "mistakenly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.852,
    "endTime": 391.606,
    "text": "I opened the letter,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 391.606,
    "endTime": 397.518,
    "text": "and it informed me that David Irving was bringing a libel suit against me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.518,
    "endTime": 399.13899999999995,
    "text": "in the United Kingdom"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 399.139,
    "endTime": 402.833,
    "text": "for calling him a Holocaust denier."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.833,
    "endTime": 404.79100000000005,
    "text": "David Irving suing me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.791,
    "endTime": 406.019,
    "text": "Who was David Irving?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406.019,
    "endTime": 408.65,
    "text": "David Irving was a writer of historical works,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.65,
    "endTime": 410.697,
    "text": "most of them about World War II,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.697,
    "endTime": 413.94,
    "text": "and virtually all of those works took the position"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413.94,
    "endTime": 417.542,
    "text": "that the Nazis were really not so bad,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.542,
    "endTime": 420.65,
    "text": "and the allies were really not so good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 420.65,
    "endTime": 422.779,
    "text": "And the Jews, whatever happened to them,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 422.779,
    "endTime": 425.086,
    "text": "they sort of deserved it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 425.086,
    "endTime": 426.601,
    "text": "He knew the documents,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 426.601,
    "endTime": 428.068,
    "text": "he knew the facts,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.068,
    "endTime": 431.89599999999996,
    "text": "but he somehow twisted them to get this opinion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.896,
    "endTime": 434.432,
    "text": "He hadn't always been a Holocaust denier,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 434.432,
    "endTime": 436.197,
    "text": "but in the late '80s,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436.197,
    "endTime": 440.397,
    "text": "he embraced it with great vigor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.397,
    "endTime": 444.32599999999996,
    "text": "The reason I laughed also was this was a man"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.326,
    "endTime": 446.28400000000005,
    "text": "who not only was a Holocaust denier,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 446.284,
    "endTime": 448.003,
    "text": "but seemed quite proud of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.003,
    "endTime": 449.651,
    "text": "Here was a man -- and I quote --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 449.651,
    "endTime": 454.225,
    "text": "who said, \"I'm going to sink the battleship Auschwitz.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 454.225,
    "endTime": 455.42100000000005,
    "text": "Here was a man"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 455.421,
    "endTime": 460.596,
    "text": "who pointed to the number tattooed on a survivor's arm and said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 460.596,
    "endTime": 462.212,
    "text": "\"How much money have you made"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 462.212,
    "endTime": 466.429,
    "text": "from having that number tattooed on your arm?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 466.429,
    "endTime": 468.361,
    "text": "Here was a man who said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 468.361,
    "endTime": 471.341,
    "text": "\"More people died in Senator Kennedy's car"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471.341,
    "endTime": 472.677,
    "text": "at Chappaquiddick"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.677,
    "endTime": 476.01500000000004,
    "text": "than died in gas chambers at Auschwitz.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 476.015,
    "endTime": 480.286,
    "text": "That's an American reference, but you can look it up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 480.286,
    "endTime": 483.324,
    "text": "This was not a man who seemed at all ashamed or reticent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 483.324,
    "endTime": 486.016,
    "text": "about being a Holocaust denier."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 486.016,
    "endTime": 489.82,
    "text": "Now, lots of my academic colleagues counseled me --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489.82,
    "endTime": 491.75,
    "text": "\"Eh, Deborah, just ignore it.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 491.75,
    "endTime": 495.362,
    "text": "When I explained you can't just ignore a libel suit,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 495.362,
    "endTime": 498.663,
    "text": "they said, \"Who's going to believe him anyway?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498.663,
    "endTime": 500.767,
    "text": "But here was the problem:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 500.767,
    "endTime": 506.099,
    "text": "British law put the onus, put the burden of proof on me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 506.099,
    "endTime": 508.805,
    "text": "to prove the truth of what I said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 508.805,
    "endTime": 511.592,
    "text": "in contrast to as it would have been in the United States"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511.592,
    "endTime": 513.12,
    "text": "and in many other countries:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 513.12,
    "endTime": 516.801,
    "text": "on him to prove the falsehood."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 516.801,
    "endTime": 518.2860000000001,
    "text": "What did that mean?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.286,
    "endTime": 521.6859999999999,
    "text": "That meant if I didn't fight,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 521.686,
    "endTime": 524.671,
    "text": "he would win by default."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 524.671,
    "endTime": 526.45,
    "text": "And if he won by default,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 526.45,
    "endTime": 529.115,
    "text": "he could then legitimately say,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 529.115,
    "endTime": 534.475,
    "text": "\"My David Irving version of the Holocaust is a legitimate version."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.475,
    "endTime": 536.683,
    "text": "Deborah Lipstadt was found to have libeled me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 536.683,
    "endTime": 538.654,
    "text": "when she called me a Holocaust denier."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 538.654,
    "endTime": 543.106,
    "text": "Ipso facto, I, David Irving, am not a Holocaust denier.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 543.106,
    "endTime": 545.311,
    "text": "And what is that version?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 545.311,
    "endTime": 548.331,
    "text": "There was no plan to murder the Jews,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 548.331,
    "endTime": 550.407,
    "text": "there were no gas chambers,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 550.407,
    "endTime": 552.287,
    "text": "there were no mass shootings,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 552.287,
    "endTime": 555.4820000000001,
    "text": "Hitler had nothing to do with any suffering that went on,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 555.482,
    "endTime": 559.3109999999999,
    "text": "and the Jews have made this all up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559.311,
    "endTime": 561.7330000000001,
    "text": "to get money from Germany"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 561.733,
    "endTime": 563.4639999999999,
    "text": "and to get a state,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 563.464,
    "endTime": 566.865,
    "text": "and they've done it with the aid and abettance of the allies --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 566.865,
    "endTime": 571.34,
    "text": "they've planted the documents and planted the evidence."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 571.34,
    "endTime": 573.744,
    "text": "I couldn't let that stand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 573.744,
    "endTime": 576.703,
    "text": "and ever face a survivor"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 576.703,
    "endTime": 578.702,
    "text": "or a child of survivors."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 578.702,
    "endTime": 580.878,
    "text": "I couldn't let that stand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 580.878,
    "endTime": 586.067,
    "text": "and consider myself a responsible historian."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 586.067,
    "endTime": 587.836,
    "text": "So we fought."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.836,
    "endTime": 590.142,
    "text": "And for those of you who haven't seen \"Denial,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 590.142,
    "endTime": 591.325,
    "text": "spoiler alert:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.325,
    "endTime": 592.567,
    "text": "we won."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 592.567,
    "endTime": 593.886,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593.886,
    "endTime": 600.8679999999999,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600.868,
    "endTime": 605.133,
    "text": "The judge found David Irving"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 605.133,
    "endTime": 608.488,
    "text": "to be a liar,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 608.488,
    "endTime": 609.6750000000001,
    "text": "a racist,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.675,
    "endTime": 610.953,
    "text": "an anti-Semite."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 610.953,
    "endTime": 613.337,
    "text": "His view of history was tendentious,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 613.337,
    "endTime": 615.287,
    "text": "he lied, he distorted --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 615.287,
    "endTime": 617.9540000000001,
    "text": "and most importantly,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 617.954,
    "endTime": 620.0909999999999,
    "text": "he did it deliberately."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 620.091,
    "endTime": 624.254,
    "text": "We showed a pattern, in over 25 different major instances."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.254,
    "endTime": 627.388,
    "text": "Not small things -- many of us in this audience write books,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 627.388,
    "endTime": 628.597,
    "text": "are writing books;"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 628.597,
    "endTime": 632.087,
    "text": "we always make mistakes, that's why we're glad to have second editions:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 632.087,
    "endTime": 633.297,
    "text": "correct the mistakes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 633.297,
    "endTime": 635.514,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 635.514,
    "endTime": 639.498,
    "text": "But these always moved in the same direction:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 639.498,
    "endTime": 641.7330000000001,
    "text": "blame the Jews,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 641.733,
    "endTime": 644.5799999999999,
    "text": "exonerate the Nazis."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 644.58,
    "endTime": 647.076,
    "text": "But how did we win?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.076,
    "endTime": 653.07,
    "text": "What we did is follow his footnotes back to his sources."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 653.07,
    "endTime": 654.8770000000001,
    "text": "And what did we find?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 654.877,
    "endTime": 656.38,
    "text": "Not in most cases,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 656.38,
    "endTime": 658.372,
    "text": "and not in the preponderance of cases,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 658.372,
    "endTime": 662.707,
    "text": "but in every single instance where he made some reference to the Holocaust,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 662.707,
    "endTime": 666.973,
    "text": "that his supposed evidence was distorted,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 666.973,
    "endTime": 668.4169999999999,
    "text": "half-truth,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 668.417,
    "endTime": 669.775,
    "text": "date-changed,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 669.775,
    "endTime": 671.986,
    "text": "sequence-changed,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 671.986,
    "endTime": 674.134,
    "text": "someone put at a meeting who wasn't there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 674.134,
    "endTime": 676.919,
    "text": "In other words, he didn't have the evidence."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 676.919,
    "endTime": 679.052,
    "text": "His evidence didn't prove it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 679.052,
    "endTime": 682.508,
    "text": "We didn't prove what happened."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 682.508,
    "endTime": 685.0310000000001,
    "text": "We proved that what he said happened --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.031,
    "endTime": 687.915,
    "text": "and by extension, all deniers, because he either quotes them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 687.915,
    "endTime": 690.41,
    "text": "or they get their arguments from him --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 690.41,
    "endTime": 691.68,
    "text": "is not true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 691.68,
    "endTime": 692.8929999999999,
    "text": "What they claim --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 692.893,
    "endTime": 697.489,
    "text": "they don't have the evidence to prove it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 697.489,
    "endTime": 702.2570000000001,
    "text": "So why is my story more than just the story"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 702.257,
    "endTime": 706.088,
    "text": "of a quirky, long, six-year, difficult lawsuit,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 706.088,
    "endTime": 711.101,
    "text": "an American professor being dragged into a courtroom"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 711.101,
    "endTime": 714.169,
    "text": "by a man that the court declared in its judgment"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 714.169,
    "endTime": 716.443,
    "text": "was a Neo-Nazi polemicist?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 716.443,
    "endTime": 718.68,
    "text": "What message does it have?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 718.68,
    "endTime": 721.6769999999999,
    "text": "I think in the context of the question of truth,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 721.677,
    "endTime": 724.163,
    "text": "it has a very significant message."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 724.163,
    "endTime": 725.972,
    "text": "Because today,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 725.972,
    "endTime": 727.662,
    "text": "as we well know,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 727.662,
    "endTime": 732.582,
    "text": "truth and facts are under assault."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 732.582,
    "endTime": 735.858,
    "text": "Social media, for all the gifts it has given us,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 735.858,
    "endTime": 741.463,
    "text": "has also allowed the difference between facts -- established facts --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 741.463,
    "endTime": 743.2439999999999,
    "text": "and lies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 743.244,
    "endTime": 745.87,
    "text": "to be flattened."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 745.87,
    "endTime": 747.404,
    "text": "Third of all:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 747.404,
    "endTime": 749.592,
    "text": "extremism."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 749.592,
    "endTime": 753.468,
    "text": "You may not see Ku Klux Klan robes,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 753.468,
    "endTime": 755.563,
    "text": "you may not see burning crosses,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 755.563,
    "endTime": 759.906,
    "text": "you may not even hear outright white supremacist language."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 759.906,
    "endTime": 764.8359999999999,
    "text": "It may go by names: \"alt-right,\" \"National Front\" -- pick your names."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 764.836,
    "endTime": 770.695,
    "text": "But underneath, it's that same extremism that I found in Holocaust denial"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 770.695,
    "endTime": 776.014,
    "text": "parading as rational discourse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 776.014,
    "endTime": 781.255,
    "text": "We live in an age where truth is on the defensive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 781.255,
    "endTime": 783.763,
    "text": "I'm reminded of a New Yorker cartoon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 783.763,
    "endTime": 786.307,
    "text": "A quiz show recently appeared in \"The New Yorker\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 786.307,
    "endTime": 789.553,
    "text": "where the host of the quiz show is saying to one of the contestants,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 789.553,
    "endTime": 791.886,
    "text": "\"Yes, ma'am, you had the right answer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 791.886,
    "endTime": 794.403,
    "text": "But your opponent yelled more loudly than you did,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 794.403,
    "endTime": 797.1080000000001,
    "text": "so he gets the point.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 797.108,
    "endTime": 799.4369999999999,
    "text": "What can we do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 799.437,
    "endTime": 800.838,
    "text": "First of all,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 800.838,
    "endTime": 806.293,
    "text": "we cannot be beguiled by rational appearances."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 806.293,
    "endTime": 808.086,
    "text": "We've got to look underneath,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 808.086,
    "endTime": 811.871,
    "text": "and we will find there the extremism."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 811.871,
    "endTime": 813.881,
    "text": "Second of all,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 813.881,
    "endTime": 822.0169999999999,
    "text": "we must understand that truth is not relative."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 822.017,
    "endTime": 823.5050000000001,
    "text": "Number three,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 823.505,
    "endTime": 827.218,
    "text": "we must go on the offensive,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 827.218,
    "endTime": 829.5559999999999,
    "text": "not the defensive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 829.556,
    "endTime": 832.187,
    "text": "When someone makes an outrageous claim,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 832.187,
    "endTime": 835.715,
    "text": "even though they may hold one of the highest offices in the land,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 835.715,
    "endTime": 837.75,
    "text": "if not the world --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 837.75,
    "endTime": 839.284,
    "text": "we must say to them,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 839.284,
    "endTime": 841.274,
    "text": "\"Where's the proof?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 841.274,
    "endTime": 843.435,
    "text": "Where's the evidence?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 843.435,
    "endTime": 846.386,
    "text": "We must hold their feet to the fire."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 846.386,
    "endTime": 852.275,
    "text": "We must not treat it as if their lies are the same as the facts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 852.275,
    "endTime": 855.8389999999999,
    "text": "And as I said earlier, truth is not relative."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 855.839,
    "endTime": 858.719,
    "text": "Many of us have grown up in the world of the academy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 858.719,
    "endTime": 860.484,
    "text": "and enlightened liberal thought,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 860.484,
    "endTime": 864.044,
    "text": "where we're taught everything is open to debate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 864.044,
    "endTime": 866.082,
    "text": "But that's not the case."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 866.082,
    "endTime": 870.072,
    "text": "There are certain things that are true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 870.072,
    "endTime": 873.116,
    "text": "There are indisputable facts --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 873.116,
    "endTime": 875.399,
    "text": "objective truths."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 875.399,
    "endTime": 880.24,
    "text": "Galileo taught it to us centuries ago."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 880.24,
    "endTime": 884.931,
    "text": "Even after being forced to recant by the Vatican"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 884.931,
    "endTime": 887.528,
    "text": "that the Earth moved around the Sun,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 887.528,
    "endTime": 888.706,
    "text": "he came out,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 888.706,
    "endTime": 891.04,
    "text": "and what is he reported to have said?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 891.04,
    "endTime": 896.222,
    "text": "\"And yet, it still moves.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 896.222,
    "endTime": 899.086,
    "text": "The Earth is not flat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 899.086,
    "endTime": 902.267,
    "text": "The climate is changing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 902.267,
    "endTime": 904.5590000000001,
    "text": "Elvis is not alive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 904.559,
    "endTime": 906.1179999999999,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 906.118,
    "endTime": 908.4580000000001,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 908.458,
    "endTime": 910.783,
    "text": "And most importantly,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 910.783,
    "endTime": 916.169,
    "text": "truth and fact are under assault."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 916.169,
    "endTime": 917.803,
    "text": "The job ahead of us,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 917.803,
    "endTime": 919.03,
    "text": "the task ahead of us,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 919.03,
    "endTime": 920.648,
    "text": "the challenge ahead of us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 920.648,
    "endTime": 922.6270000000001,
    "text": "is great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 922.627,
    "endTime": 926.121,
    "text": "The time to fight is short."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 926.121,
    "endTime": 929.809,
    "text": "We must act now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 929.809,
    "endTime": 933.078,
    "text": "Later will be too late."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 933.078,
    "endTime": 934.3639999999999,
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 934.364,
    "endTime": 944.364,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  }
]